capstone.data

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • capstone.data.Data
      • capstone.data.Profile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Profile
extends Data
    A data-class to model a user-profile. Such a user-profile consists of an ID, a Real Name, a KeyMap (mapping InputKeys to Directions) and lastly a Representation.
    See Also:
